Getting YouTube Transcripts: 3 Methods, Ranked by Ease
Method 1: youtube-transcript-api (Free, No API Key Needed) — Best Starting Point
This is the fastest and most reliable free method.
bashpip install youtube-transcript-api
pythonfrom youtube_transcript_api import YouTubeTranscriptApi

# Single video
